{{infobox Organization |name = Bund Deutscher Holzwirte e.V. |image = |caption = |abbreviation = BDH |formation = 1950 |purpose = Professional association |location = {{flagicon|DE}} [[Hamburg]], [[Germany]] | |region_served = Germany |leader_title = Chairman |leader_name = [[Malte Jörn Krafft]] |website = [https://www.holzwirte.com/ www.holzwirte.com] }}
'''Bund Deutscher Holzwirte''' (BDH) (English: Association of German Wood Scientists) is a [[professional association|professional]] and [[alumni association]] for graduates of the German degree course for Holzwirtschaft (English: Wood Science), founded in 1950.
==History== The BDH was founded on 22 July 1950 in Hamburg (Germany) by graduates of the degree program for Holzwirtschaft.<ref>{{cite web|title=Stiftung Holzwirtschaft|periodical=|publisher=|url=https://www.holzwirte.com/stiftung-holzwirtschaft.html|deadurl=|format=|accessdate=2018-03-23|archiveurl=|archivedate=|last=|date=|year=|month=|day=|language=German|pages=|quote=}}</ref> This course of study was established in 1939 by the Reichsinstitut für ausländische und koloniale Forstwirtschaft (English: Reich Institute for Foreign and Colonial Forestry). As of 1946 the [[University of Hamburg]] continues the course.<ref>{{cite web|title=Franz Heske und die Gründung des „Reichsintitutes für ausländische und koloniale Forstwirtschaft in Schloss Reinbek, 1931 bis 1940/42“|periodical=|publisher=|url=https://www.holzwirte.com/files/Downloads/Sonstiges/Vortrag%20Bavendamm%20Langfassung_75%20Jahre%20Studium.pdf|deadurl=|format=PDF; 280 kB|accessdate=2018-03-23|archiveurl=|archivedate=|last=Dirk Bavendamm|date=2014|year=|month=|day=|language=German|pages=|quote=}}</ref>
==Purpose== The purpose of the BDH is 'to promote [[wood economy]] by exchanging professional experiences as well as maintaining personal contacts of the members, to support the professional development of the members and to inform about the degree program for Holzwirtschaft' (translated paragraph of the statutes).<ref>{{cite web|title=Satzung des Bundes Deutscher Holzwirte|periodical=|publisher=|url=https://www.holzwirte.com/satzung.html|deadurl=|format=|accessdate=2018-03-23|archiveurl=|archivedate=|last=|date=|year=|month=|day=|language=German|pages=|quote=}}</ref>
